{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-templates-post-tsx","path":"/blog/bfbb5f42-1a50-53b3-9a85-bd0c7afc5e0d/","result":{"data":{"post":{"frontmatter":{"date":"21 Jul 2025","title":"Microsoft Authenticator ends password support","text":"What's going on? Autofill is now disabled in Microsoft Authenticator app. In August, all stored passwords and payment methods will be removed automatically. MFA and passkeys will work as usual.","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/c7240/BlogMicrosoft.png","srcSet":"/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/de3a1/BlogMicrosoft.png 150w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/30cdc/BlogMicrosoft.png 300w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/c7240/BlogMicrosoft.png 600w","sizes":"(min-width: 600px) 600px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/81307/BlogMicrosoft.avif 150w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/aa5b9/BlogMicrosoft.avif 300w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/0c8d0/BlogMicrosoft.avif 600w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 600px) 600px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/c65bc/BlogMicrosoft.webp 150w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/078c3/BlogMicrosoft.webp 300w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/6d09e/BlogMicrosoft.webp 600w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 600px) 600px, 100vw"}]},"width":600,"height":600}}},"keywords":["Microsoft Authenticator","private cloud","Self-hosting password manager"],"canonicalUrl":""},"html":"<h3>Microsoft Authenticator ends password support</h3>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 900px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/302a4/BlogMicrosoft.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/09011/BlogMicrosoft.avif 225w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/e46ac/BlogMicrosoft.avif 450w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/9b8d4/BlogMicrosoft.avif 900w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/d8ca6/BlogMicrosoft.avif 1080w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/d7e55/BlogMicrosoft.webp 225w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/8626f/BlogMicrosoft.webp 450w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/131f1/BlogMicrosoft.webp 900w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/260c2/BlogMicrosoft.webp 1080w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/3684f/BlogMicrosoft.png 225w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/fc2a6/BlogMicrosoft.png 450w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/1cfc2/BlogMicrosoft.png 900w,\n/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/302a4/BlogMicrosoft.png 1080w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/2260e830cddfe2f9d3ee1dcd9519d651/1cfc2/BlogMicrosoft.png\"\n            alt=\"Microsoft Authenticator\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Microsoft Authenticator</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>What's going on?</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Autofill is now disabled in Microsoft Authenticator app.</li>\n<li>In August, all stored passwords and payment methods will be removed automatically.</li>\n<li>MFA and passkeys will work as usual.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>If your team only uses Authenticator for MFA- you're fine. But users who want to continue using the passwords saved in Microsoft Authenticator for autofill will need to install Microsoft Edge on their phone.</p>\n<p>Microsoft says:</p>\n<p>\"Your saved passwords (but not your generated password history) and addresses are securely synced to your Microsoft account, and you can continue to access them and enjoy seamless autofill functionality with Microsoft Edge.\"</p>\n<p>If switching to Edge isn’t your thing, there’s still time — you can export your passwords to another manager (like Bitwarden) before they’re wiped. Just be aware: relying on external services for password management might lead to unpredictable results. Storing such critical business information is risky. <a href=\"https://blog.lastpass.com/posts/notice-of-recent-security-incident\">The LastPass breach</a> is a perfect example.</p>\n<p>Quick refresher on the 2022 LastPass incident: hackers first got in through a developer’s account, then installed a keylogger on their personal computer, which gave them access to LastPass’s cloud storage. From there, they stole encrypted password vaults and unencrypted user data. 33 million users were affected. That’s a staggering number — wild, isn’t it? Any external service becomes a single point of failure.</p>\n<p>Public services might go down unexpectedly and in the meantime you won't be able to access some password protected resources, because your password managements SaaS is unreachable. Our CTO has covered this topic in depth. Read the full article <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/salaros_privatecloud-onprem-multicloud-activity-7339210136982335488-0KF3/\">here</a>.</p>\n<h3>What can this lead to?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>loss of access to client infrastructure;</li>\n<li>team downtime;</li>\n<li>missed SLAs and contract breaches (leading to financial loss and damaged trust).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Self-hosting password manager is the ultimate solution for all these problems, but you need help of an IT professional to set it up and keep it up to date and secure. That’s where we come in.</p>\n<p>We help businesses build a secure, unified environment for identity, access, and apps — so you're ready for whatever changes come next. <a href=\"https://www.codecave.it/#contact-form\">Let’s talk</a> and stay one step ahead.</p>","wordCount":{"words":350}},"author":{"frontmatter":{"authorAlias":"Zakruzhnaya","author":"Olga Zakruzhnaya","authorPosition":"Marketing specialist","authorPhoto":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/d4a57/author.jpg","srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/40657/author.jpg 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/77b35/author.jpg 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/d4a57/author.jpg 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/19e71/author.jpg 128w","sizes":"(min-width: 64px) 64px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/e8e20/author.avif 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/b6d61/author.avif 32w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/2e71d/author.avif 64w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/3c49f/author.avif 128w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 64px) 64px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/906692340e07de91d933684326227c1c/e789a/author.webp 16w,\n/static/906692340e07de91d933684